You can see Sapporo Snow Festival for seven days in February.
You can see a lot of beautiful and wonderful ice sculptures at that festival.
There are eight popular ramen shops.
Because of the cold weather, rich ramen soup is popular in Sapporo.
If you visit Sapporo Snow Festival at night, you can enjoy seeing the ice sculptures with the lights.
We are sure that you will love Sapporo ramen.
If you want to eat delicious ramen, you should go to Ramen Kyowakoku.
It is near Sapporo Station.
It is a five-minute walk from the station.
There are eight popular ramen shops in Ramen Kyowakoku.
Because of the cold weather, rich ramen soup is popular in Sapporo.
We are sure that you will love Sapporo ramen.
